body:
Star Guardian Ahri&#039;s taunt responses don&#039;t seem to trigger... ever. I&#039;ve stood beside teammates and had them taunt me, been close to enemies in lane and had them taunt me, and I never ever hear her taunt responses (which is sad because they&#039;re so sassy!) {{sticker:sg-ahri-3}} 
I&#039;m not sure if they&#039;re just super duper quiet, or they aren&#039;t triggering at all.
Also, her charm lines, ability lines, and kill lines are _extremely_ quiet compared to her movement and attack lines. I really really have to listen out for them if I want to listen to what she&#039;s saying. And her charm ones especially are unintelligible.
Please fix this soon! :D Her voice work is so wonderful it&#039;d be such a shame to miss out on so much wonderfulness. {{sticker:sg-ahri-2}}
